<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Oxford College will grant up to 16 hours of AP credit according to the following guidelines: 4 credit hours for scores of 4 or 5 on exams.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://oxford.emory.edu/academics/catalog/admission/advanced-academic-credit/" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

